::Skulletron::

	Skulletron was getting tired of doing gaurd duty.  He wanted to get that
cloaked intruder so he could go do something else.  Although he wouldn't
admit it to her, he was already starting to miss the pleasure of Feline
being there.  He was thinking about her, walking along, hips swaying, tail
moving around gracefully.  He couldn't stop thinking about her.  But, he
did, and now he was still bored.  He couldn't wait to nab that intruder. 
That's when he could go disturb some bots' emotions!
